      "content": "but that's just what people say to be nice. if you actually look at the numbers... the cost of my healthcare, the food, the just existing... it's all coming out of their future. i'm literally taking away from them every single day. like, how is it 'being a parent' if i'm just a leak in their boat? it just feels like if i wasn't here, that weight would just lift and they could actually breathe.",
